{"tid":238871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得地鐵敬老敬到有d離譜","createTime":"2017-05-11T09:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T11:43:02.000Z","uid":36502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3c3e06c2ffafe070a1d15403b872ee83ac1c4a","tid":238871,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"話說係藍田站，每層扶手電梯都有2-3個地鐵職員看守住，當發現有老人家，2個就會狗衝，一前一後夾住個老人家，保護住個老人家上落扶手電梯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不嬲都冇乜所謂，反正你on9都唔關我事。<br />\n但最近變本加厲，除左2個夾住之外，仲要加埋封鎖後排，唔比其他人上落，直到果個老人家上左十秒左右時間，才解封後排手。<br />\n<br />\n久而久之，藍田地鐵站係放工時間人塞夜塞，多人過年宵。<br />\n<br />\n想問地鐵一句，其實你係咪on9架，夾住個老人家有撚用阿，你果2個員工又唔係扶實個老人家，個老人家要跌都係層層疊架啦。<br />\n仲有，封鎖後排個諗法，係咪覺得個老人家係炸彈，唔比人行近？係就唔該封鎖耐d，直到個老人家上哂去先解封。<br />\n<br />\n最後，屌你老母死港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58adcdd9221ed39919313132855def3f9751e747","tid":238871,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申住藍田"},{"pid":"8d0738b13dfcb886c98af808241a413897712d69","tid":238871,"uid":5851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a73338a61b4c7d033d25bd92fbbb3220f52be7","tid":238871,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"強烈要求港鐵係返工/放工時段，暫停夾老人活動"},{"pid":"0d87a8a5e1ec37628188d178f33aa913b2224018","tid":238871,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7210d3654a10709b3cd1adf6658517c3be9ae96","tid":238871,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:40:24.000Z"